      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1) in concours condition. This specimen features the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six, delivering 355 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a factory-spec Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system. The chassis remains factory-rigid, complemented by four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors with zero lipping. The cabin exhibits no bolster wear on the leather sport seats, and the dash is free of UV degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver's car with a comprehensive service dossier and original VIN-matched panels.",
